See the following.  TreeMap works, HashMap doesn't:
```scala
cala> var m = Map.empty[Int, Int]                                 
m: scala.collection.immutable.Map[Int,Int] = Map()

scala> for(i <- 1 until 40000; j <- 1 until 500) m = m.update(j, i)
